{{Expand Romanian|Titus Munteanu|date=December 2013}} {{Infobox person | name = Titus Munteanu | image = | imagesize = | caption = | birth_name = Titus Munteanu | birth_date = {{birth date|1941|10|3|df=yes}} | birth_place = | death_date = {{death date and age|2013|12|18|1941|10|3|df=yes}} | death_place = [[Bucharest]], [[Romania]] | other_names = | alma_mater = | occupation = Director, filmmaker, producer | spouse = | children = | website = | years_active = 1966–2013 }}
'''Titus Munteanu''' (3 October 1941 − 18 December 2013) was a [[Romania]]n director, filmmaker and producer.
Munteanu began his television career in 1966 and was best known for his work with the broadcaster [[TVR 1]].
In 2004, Munteanu received the Excellence Award from [[National Audiovisual Council]] ({{lang-ro|Consiliul Național al Audiovizualului}}, CNA).<ref>[http://www.mediafax.ro/cultura-media/alexandru-arsinel-titus-munteanu-a-fost-un-lansator-de-vedete-regret-enorm-disparitia-lui-11790810 Alexandru Arşinel: Titus Munteanu a fost un lansator de vedete. Regret enorm dispariţia lui] {{ro icon}}</ref>
Titus Munteanu died of [[respiratory disease]] on 18 December 2013, aged 72, in [[Bucharest]], [[Romania]].<ref>[http://www.digi24.ro/Stiri/Digi24/Actualitate/Stiri/A+murit+realizatorul+de+televiziune+Titus+Munteanu A murit realizatorul de televiziune Titus Munteanu] {{ro icon}}</ref>
